# Token economy + model routing

Canonical config: `.orchestrator/config/models.json` and `config/policies.json`.

## Caveman

Default **full**: terse replies, no filler. Keep code, paths, errors exact. Off only if user says stop caveman / normal mode.

## Model by task class

| Task class | Tier | Prefer (Cursor) |
|---|---|---|
| trivial / classify | fast | `claude-4.5-haiku` |
| docs / documentation / implementation | balanced | `claude-sonnet-5-thinking-high` |
| architecture / hard debug | deep | `claude-opus-4-8-thinking-high` |
| complex_analysis / long_agentic / orchestration_plan | max | `claude-fable-5-thinking-high` |
| mechanical edits | fast | `composer-2.5-fast` |

Never use Fable/Opus for docs or typos. Escalate at most one tier after failed validation.
